title: Bug 132103 - No objects under Context in palette when scripting a data set
description: When scripting a data set, the Context palette does not display any objects.
OB: No objects are visible under the 'Context' section in the palette while scripting a data set.
EB: Expected behavior is that relevant objects under the 'Context' section should be displayed in the palette when scripting a data set.
SR:
1. Open the scripting interface for a data set.
2. Navigate to the 'Context' section in the palette.
3. Observe that no objects are displayed.
